<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Madlib in Love</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/style.css"> 

  </head>
  
  <body>
    <h1>MadLib in Love</h1>

    <form method="POST" action="/results">
      
      First Name: 
      <input type="text" name="first_name">
      Last Name: 
      <input type="text" name="last_name">
      <br>
      <input type="radio" name="gender" value="male">Male
      <input type="radio" name="gender" value="female">Female
      <br>
      Question 1: Who would you most trust with your firstborn child?
      <br>
      <input type="radio" name="q1" value="1">A
      <input type="radio" name="q1" value="2">B
      <input type="radio" name="q1" value="3">C
      <input type="radio" name="q1" value="4">D
      <br>
      Question 2: On a typical friday night, you are most likely:
      <br>
      <input type="radio" name="q2" value="1">A
      <input type="radio" name="q2" value="2">B
      <input type="radio" name="q2" value="3">C
      <input type="radio" name="q2" value="4">D
      <br>
      Question 3: If you could go back in time and have dinner with 1 person, who would it be?
      <br>
      <input type="radio" name="q3" value="1">A
      <input type="radio" name="q3" value="2">B
      <input type="radio" name="q3" value="3">C
      <input type="radio" name="q3" value="4">D
      <br>
      Question 4: The best computer program ever written would do:
      <br>
      <input type="radio" name="q4" value="1">A
      <input type="radio" name="q4" value="2">B
      <input type="radio" name="q4" value="3">C
      <input type="radio" name="q4" value="4">D
      <br>
      <input type="submit" value="Find my Dream Date!">

    </form>  
  </body>
</html>